snippet.title: Jeebo & Jerbo vs. Life Chapter 1: Jeebo & Jerbo vs. The Dream Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Jeebo & Jerbo vs. Life is a video game developed by StegTech LLC. It is a story-based Metroidvania/JRPG. Chapter 1, Jeebo & Jerbo vs. The Dream is coming out this October.
